txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Broken wooden clubs from the sentient enemies of the Free Peoples. Deliver the items to Maegamiel at Echad Mirobel in the southern section of Eregion.
'The enemies of the Free Peoples must continue to fall, or all will be lost. Thank you.'

'Men of the north, Orcs from the south and north, and the vile union of the two now comb this land that was once our home. We must drive them back. Collect their weapons and sheaths, whatever they many be, and deliver them to me for a reward.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Broken Wooden Clubs
Maegamiel at Echad Mirobel has requested that broken wooden clubs be delivered to her at the Elf-ruins in the southern reaches of Eregion.
Deliver the broken wooden clubs to Maegamiel at Echad Mirobel in southern Eregion
You have accepted a task to deliver broken wooden clubs taken from the enemies of the Free Peoples to Maegamiel. Maegamiel defends Echad Mirobel in the southern area of Eregion.
Wanted: Broken wooden clubs from the sentient enemies of the Free Peoples.
